title: 3D Artist Issue 64 - 2014  UK
description:
3D Artist Issue 64 - 2014  UK

116 Pages | True PDF | English | 16 MB 


3D Artist magazine is a luxury title for fans of 3D software and the phenomenal images that can be created. Each issue is packed with advice and inspiration for 3D devotees, all written by first-class artists. The tutorials give readers valuable insight into the techniques used by 3D professionals, while interviews and features focus on the latest projects being created by commercial studios and freelancers.
